formatAction

public java.lang.String formatAction()
Formats action, and returns a proper String. Some actions have a parameter, e.g. the row Id of a building or player, or any other object. For thoses actions, the object is loaded from the DB and some fields are used, e.g. name of the building.

Returns:
formated String
